        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-24f36f38-ba85-4d55-9dff-5757339a45a5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-24f36f38-ba85-4d55-9dff-5757339a45a5">
                Mr. Tinker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-24f36f38-ba85-4d55-9dff-5757339a45a5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-02-20/debates/fdabc121-2694-4948-9fed-c10238adff41/DefenceLoans#contribution-24f36f38-ba85-4d55-9dff-5757339a45a5">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of Order, Sir Dennis. There are three Amendments to the Resolution on the Order Paper, and I should be obliged if you would give me guidance as to whether you intend to call all three Amendments or not.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-24f36f38-ba85-4d55-9dff-5757339a45a5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-02-20/debates/fdabc121-2694-4948-9fed-c10238adff41/DefenceLoans#contribution-24f36f38-ba85-4d55-9dff-5757339a45a5">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-d8bd2a22-ce7e-421e-81cb-8a8b203fb384">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-d8bd2a22-ce7e-421e-81cb-8a8b203fb384">
