                Mr. Batey
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cdba6c02-73a0-4e7a-8208-adb720fee806" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-02-20/debates/fdabc121-2694-4948-9fed-c10238adff41/DefenceLoans#contribution-cdba6c02-73a0-4e7a-8208-adb720fee806">
