<p class="">Can the hon. Member say what amount of the £90,000,000 was contributed by the estates of £50,000 and upwards?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6c6254f8-5e62-43a5-8315-d0f4223027f8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
