<p class="">May I call attention to the atrocious atmosphere in the House? Cannot something be done to improve the atmosphere and make it a little more breathable?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-fe30b5a5-65e7-446e-8c24-e95a5e6d3009" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
