    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Do the right hon. and gallant Gentleman's remarks apply to the aircraft industry as well, in which the bulk of the work must necessarily be Government work?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ef8662b8-2a16-45c9-8e0e-5c3ca4a1a039" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
