            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c5c0d9be-5f77-4dd7-8f09-776307f9ce02" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
